**Files created:**
- `internal/store/store.go` — Store package with `ValidateName`, `ListSummary`/`ListAll`, `CreateList`, `RenameList`, `DeleteList`, `CountTodos`
- `internal/store/store_test.go` — 13 tests covering all store operations and edge cases
